```{r gallbladder 32799793, include=FALSE}

PMID_32799793 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32799793', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32799793 <- paste0(PMID_32799793$journal,' ', PMID_32799793$year, ' ', PMID_32799793$month,';', PMID_32799793$volume,'(', PMID_32799793$number,'):', PMID_32799793$pages)

PubMed_32799793 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32799793$eprint)

doi_32799793 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32799793$doi)

Sys.sleep(2)
```
